---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Rustzen"
  description="Privacy policy for Zen Clear and Rustzen services."
>
  <main class="legal-page">
    <article class="legal-document">
      <p class="eyebrow">Privacy Policy</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: June 25, 2026</p>

      <p>
        Rustzen builds Zen Clear as a local-first macOS cleanup app. This policy
        explains what information is handled by the app, the Rustzen website,
        Rustzen Cloud, and our payment provider.
      </p>

      <h2>Information Zen Clear Handles Locally</h2>
      <p>
        Zen Clear scans local development, tool, cache, and system locations
        from the app's configured scan scope, rules, and exclusions. Scan
        results, paths, sizes, cleanup previews, Restore Center records, rules,
        and app settings are processed on your Mac unless a feature clearly uses
        Rustzen Cloud.
      </p>

      <h2>Information Sent To Rustzen Cloud</h2>
      <p>
        License activation and status checks may send your license key, device
        identifier, device name, product code, app version, and related license
        status metadata to Rustzen Cloud. We use this information to activate
        your license, enforce device limits, refresh subscription status, and
        provide support.
      </p>

      <h2>Payments</h2>
      <p>
        Checkout, payment details, subscription billing, receipts, and payment
        account information are processed by Creem. Rustzen receives the
        transaction, subscription, customer email, and license information needed
        to fulfill Zen Clear Pro.
      </p>

      <h2>Website And Support</h2>
      <p>
        When you visit this website or contact support, we may receive basic
        technical information from hosting providers and the information you
        choose to provide in your message. We use it to operate the site,
        respond to requests, and improve product reliability.
      </p>

      <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        We do not sell personal information. We share information only with
        service providers needed to operate Zen Clear, Rustzen Cloud, checkout,
        hosting, analytics, customer support, legal compliance, or fraud
        prevention.
      </p>

      <h2>Retention And Requests</h2>
      <p>
        We retain license, billing, and support records for as long as needed to
        provide the service, comply with legal obligations, resolve disputes,
        and prevent abuse. To request access, correction, or deletion, contact
        <a href="mailto:support@rustzen.dev">support@rustzen.dev</a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>
</SiteLayout>
